# Edoror Judy poverty Eradication and Empowerment Foundation

This repository contains the source code for the official website of the **Edoror Judy Poverty Eradication and Empowerment Foundation (EJPEEF)**. The website provides information about the foundation’s programs, impact stories, donation options, and ways to get involved.

